{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"I’ve been on a kick lately about saying no to things. Apparently I’ve been pushed to my limit and can’t handle anything else so everything is turning into a no. But I still feel like a jerk for saying no and I don’t like feeling like a jerk. I start to apologize for saying no when I really meant it.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/09-01-feeling-badly-about-saying-no","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"date: 2016-09-01T00:05:16-05:00"}],"metadata":{"color":{"standardColorIdentifier":"purple"},"modules":[{"name":"Brunow"}],"platforms":[{"name":"Brunow","introducedAt":"2017.01.20"}],"title":"Feeling Badly About Saying No"},"topicSectionsStyle":"detailedGrid","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/2016"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/brunow\/09-01-feeling-badly-about-saying-no"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"David Brunow, known as Brunow [ˈbɹunoʊ] to the folks he works with, is a human living on Earth. You might have something in common with him — if you think it is ridiculous that he is talking about himself in the first person here, so does he."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow","url":"\/documentation\/brunow","title":"Brunow","type":"topic"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/Brunow/Archive":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"All posts"}],"role":"collectionGroup","identifier":"doc:\/\/Brunow\/documentation\/Brunow\/Archive","url":"\/documentation\/brunow\/archive","title":"Archive","type":"topic","kind":"article"},"doc://Brunow/documentation/B